name: AddChildCollection
query: mutation AddChildCollection($id: String!, $collectionId: String!) { content { collection { addChildCollection(id: $id, collectionId: $collectionId) { id } } } }

name: AddChildMetadata
query: mutation AddChildMetadata($id: String!, $metadataId: String!) { content { collection { addChildMetadata(id: $id, metadataId: $metadataId) { id } } } }

name: AddCollection
query: mutation AddCollection($collection: CollectionInput!) { content { collection { add(collection: $collection) { id } } } }

name: AddMetadata
query: mutation AddMetadata($metadata: MetadataInput!) { content { metadata { add(metadata: $metadata) { id } } } }

name: AddMetadataBulk
query: mutation AddMetadataBulk($metadatas: [MetadataChildInput!]!) { content { metadata { addBulk(metadatas: $metadatas) { id } } } }

name: AddMetadataSupplementary
query: mutation AddMetadataSupplementary($supplementary: MetadataSupplementaryInput!) { content { metadata { addSupplementary(supplementary: $supplementary) { key } } } }

name: AddSearchDocuments
query: mutation AddSearchDocuments($storageSystemId: String!, $documents: [SearchDocumentInput!]!) { content { metadata { addSearchDocuments( storageSystemId: $storageSystemId, documents: $documents) } } }

name: GetCollection
query: query GetCollection($id: String!) { content { collection(id: $id) { id name created modified labels attributes } } }

name: EnqueueChildWorkflow
query: mutation EnqueueChildWorkflow($jobId: WorkflowExecutionIdInput!, $workflowId: String!, $configurations: [WorkflowConfigurationInput!]!) { workflows { enqueueChildWorkflow(jobId: $jobId, workflowId: $workflowId, configurations: $configurations) { id queue } } }

name: EnqueueChildWorkflows
query: mutation EnqueueChildWorkflows($jobId: WorkflowExecutionIdInput!, $workflowIds: [String!]!) { workflows { enqueueChildWorkflows(jobId: $jobId, workflowIds: $workflowIds) { id queue } } }

name: EnqueueJob
query: mutation EnqueueJob($planId: WorkflowExecutionIdInput!, $jobIndex: Int!) { workflows { enqueueJob(planId: $planId, jobIndex: $jobIndex) { id queue } } }

name: FindCollection
query: query FindCollection($attributes: [FindAttributeInput!]!) { content { findCollection(attributes: $attributes) { id name created modified labels attributes type } } }

name: FindMetadata
query: query FindMetadata($attributes: [FindAttributeInput!]!) { content { findMetadata(attributes: $attributes) { id languageTag name version traitIds content { type length } created modified labels attributes source { id identifier } supplementary { key uploaded content { type length } source { id identifier } } } } }

name: GetCollectionItems
query: query GetCollectionItems($id: String!, $offset: Int!, $limit: Int!) { content { collection(id: $id) { items(limit: $limit, offset: $offset) { ... on Collection { id ready workflow { state pending } } ... on Metadata { id ready workflow { state pending } } __typename } } } }

name: Login
query: query Login($identifier: String!, $password: String!) { security { login { password(identifier: $identifier, password: $password) { principal { id } token { token } } } } }

name: GetMetadata
query: query GetMetadata($id: String!) { content { metadata(id: $id) { id languageTag name version traitIds content { type length } created modified labels attributes source { id identifier } supplementary { key uploaded content { type length } source { id identifier } } } } }

name: MetadataDownloadUrl
query: query MetadataDownloadUrl($id: String!) { content { metadata(id: $id) { content { type urls { download { url headers { name value } } } } } } }

name: MetadataUploadUrl
query: query MetadataUploadUrl($id: String!) { content { metadata(id: $id) { content { type urls { upload { url headers { name value } } } } } } }

name: Plan
query: query Plan($queue: String!) { workflows { nextWorkflowExecution(queue: $queue) { __typename ... on WorkflowJob { id { id index queue } collection { id name traitIds created modified labels attributes systemAttributes ready workflow { state pending } } metadata { id languageTag name version traitIds content { type length } created modified labels attributes systemAttributes source { id identifier } workflow { state pending } supplementary { key uploaded attributes content { type length } source { id identifier } } ready } version activity { id childWorkflowId inputs { name type } outputs { name type } configuration } context workflowActivity { id inputs { name value } outputs { name value } configuration } storageSystems { system { id type name configuration models { model { id name type configuration } configuration } } configuration } prompts { prompt { id name systemPrompt userPrompt inputType outputType } configuration } models { model { id type name configuration } configuration } } ... on WorkflowExecutionPlan { planId: id workflow { queue } next { index } } } } }

name: SetCollectionPublic

name: SetCollectionPublicList
query: mutation SetCollectionPublicList($id: String!, $public: Boolean!) { content { collection { setPublicList(id: $id, public: $public) { id } } } }

name: SetCollectionReady
query: mutation SetCollectionReady($id: String!) { content { collection { setReady(id: $id) } } }

name: SetCollectionWorkflowState
query: mutation SetCollectionWorkflowState($state: CollectionWorkflowState!) { content { collection { setWorkflowState(state: $state) } } }

name: SetCollectionWorkflowStateComplete
query: mutation SetCollectionWorkflowStateComplete($state: CollectionWorkflowCompleteState!) { content { collection { setWorkflowStateComplete(state: $state) } } }

name: SetMetadataAttributes
query: mutation SetMetadataAttributes($id: String!, $attributes: JSON!) { content { metadata { setMetadataAttributes(id: $id, attributes: $attributes) } } }

name: SetMetadataPublic
query: mutation SetMetadataPublic($id: String!, $public: Boolean!) { content { metadata { setPublic(id: $id, public: $public) { id } } } }

name: SetMetadataReady
query: mutation SetMetadataReady($id: String!) { content { metadata { setMetadataReady(id: $id) } } }

name: SetMetadataSystemAttributes
query: mutation SetMetadataSystemAttributes($id: String!, $attributes: JSON!) { content { metadata { setMetadataSystemAttributes(id: $id, attributes: $attributes) } } }

name: SetExecutionPlanJobCheckin
query: mutation SetExecutionPlanJobCheckin($jobId: WorkflowJobIdInput!) { workflows { setExecutionPlanJobCheckin(jobId: $jobId) } }

name: SetWorkflowJobComplete
query: mutation SetWorkflowJobComplete($jobId: WorkflowJobIdInput!) { workflows { setExecutionPlanJobComplete(jobId: $jobId) } }

name: SetWorkflowJobContext
query: mutation SetWorkflowJobContext($jobId: WorkflowExecutionIdInput!, $context: JSON!) { workflows { setExecutionJobContext(jobId: $jobId, context: $context) } }

name: SetWorkflowJobFailed
query: mutation SetWorkflowJobFailed($jobId: WorkflowJobIdInput!, $error: String!) { workflows { setExecutionPlanJobFailed(jobId: $jobId, error: $error) } }

name: SetWorkflowPlanContext
query: mutation SetWorkflowPlanContext($planId: WorkflowExecutionIdInput!, $context: JSON!) { workflows { setExecutionPlanContext(planId: $planId, context: $context) } }

name: SetWorkflowState
query: mutation SetWorkflowState($state: MetadataWorkflowState!) { content { metadata { setWorkflowState(state: $state) } } }

name: SetWorkflowStateComplete
query: mutation SetWorkflowStateComplete($state: MetadataWorkflowCompleteState!) { content { metadata { setWorkflowStateComplete(state: $state) } } }

name: SourceById
query: query SourceById($id: String!) { content { source(id: $id) { id name } } }

name: SupplementaryDownloadUrl
query: query SupplementaryDownloadUrl($id: String!, $key: String!) { content { metadataSupplementary(id: $id, key: $key) { metadataId key content { urls { download { url headers { name value } } } } } } }

name: SupplementaryUploadUrl
query: query SupplementaryUploadUrl($id: String!, $key: String!) { content { metadataSupplementary(id: $id, key: $key) { metadataId key content { type urls { upload { url headers { name value } } } } } } }

name: TraitById
query: query TraitById($id: String!) { content { trait(id: $id) { id workflowIds } } }
